ZH: 我的家乡在中国的西部。
EN: My hometown is in the western part of China.

ZH: 西班牙是一个美丽的国家。
EN: Spain is a beautiful country.

ZH: 西北方的天气比东南方的凉爽一些。
EN: The weather in the northwest is cooler than in the southeast.

ZH: 我们出去玩儿吧，往西走。
EN: Let's go out and head west.

ZH: 这条河流向西流。
EN: This river flows westward.

ZH: 我们住在城市的西面。
EN: We live on the west side of the city.

ZH: 西方人有些习惯和我们不一样。
EN: Westerners have some customs that are different from ours.

ZH: 今天的风向是西南风。
EN: The wind direction today is southwest.

ZH: 我在地图上找到西藏了。
EN: I found Tibet on the map.

ZH: 西门的风景比东门更美。
EN: The scenery at the west gate is more beautiful than at the east gate.

ZH: 他们选择了往西边旅行。
EN: They chose to travel towards the west.

ZH: 他的背对着西方。
EN: He has his back to the west.

ZH: 今晚的夕阳西下美丽极了。
EN: The sunset tonight is incredibly beautiful as it sets in the west.

ZH: 在冬天，傍晚的太阳总是在西边落下。
EN: In winter, the sun always sets in the west in the evening.

ZH: 这家饭店在西城。
EN: This restaurant is in the west part of the city.

ZH: 那座山峰在日落时分雄伟地耸立在西方。
EN: The mountain peak majestically stands tall in the west during sunset.

ZH: 西班牙文化非常有趣。
EN: Spanish culture is very interesting.

ZH: 我家在城里的西侧街区。
EN: My house is in the western neighborhood of the city.

ZH: 西海岸的景色真是美不胜收。
EN: The scenery on the west coast is truly breathtaking.

ZH: 再往西开一段就是边境了。
EN: If you keep heading west, you'll reach the border.
